{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"Iris","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLD8YFEiapriah27vESFSONCm4JicGMXicFgfbe3Kx7fYQicHSgCTbDdNhTzUTd00tBBS1I4enM52icFvpcQ/0","content":"权威可靠在于用事实数据说话，有相关研究说明。可疑是因为虚张声势，无实际论据支撑。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9090,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492790067000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Cora","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQOFPnicgAPH2ibVeQL1bPT5fqlt4TH87iaTrcXWB6sotemAscOSoicJSxyrM1q6NhTDzvQdMvRTQG19f/0","content":"个人认为，只有相对权威，所以很难罗列\uD83D\uDE02","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":9015,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492781622000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"络石","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKBaqg8d3cnyu0zVgMaFicsHXcc4PFsticRcqrGgQBJN5PqRjCDtnbY04Gfp0fBVwn4ibDTpluicRD31eb1kSrfsZJib/0","content":"可信权威是那些在官网如小米官网发布的一则消息，及有详细出处的，可疑权威是不正规的地方发布，列如网页就有很多","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8971,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492770609000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"iMusic","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7LhNUibskldcbw25iakOxD9tmH5sQAKkGq8HWpPakTLXgdWRqwcshCia9amXhtvvJ6kliaeTIY2vEFAH16icwsiaWINaPvZRRsWz7Nw/0","content":"可疑与可信的权威区分标准应该是这个“权威”本身的出发点、背后的组织是谁等因素。<div><br><div>可信的权威：<br><div>-在某个领域研究多年的科学家</div><div>-被权威机构认证过或获过权威奖项的专家</div><div><br></div><div>可疑的权威：</div></div><div>-广告里的专家</div><div>-某些投资机构的经济预测</div></div><div>-上级领导</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8969,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492769821000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"woody","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bTHx2ABv8mmk5Ut1KxnE0ECIx8r9hM9AFOlQ6OFAibUkXHuqoIcgicS0UVPGic7au57ibgs0dQuq4A2w/0","content":"可信权威：论文发表期刊、杂志；<div>习惯加注具体引用来源（可追溯）的媒体，例如果壳网、知乎某些回答者。</div><div><br></div><div>可疑权威：不可追溯来源的信息引用来源</div><div><br></div><div>可靠是因为有具体的具有科研精神和思考能力的专家背书；</div><div>可疑是因为不可多方验证其真实性或公正性</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8941,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492765129000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"shantaram","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icvZo6BMjoibbF7Ct6vHVL1iasrm6nsHMsXwZq9zFzuO82j7wFYx2iaXSCHk49t5Dsd3RuQdhp1t9oug/0","content":"<br>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8903,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492756724000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"海人","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoHM49jORLTQtVDTTibcOtlY8sx5w8V131rnqTyJzmlKO6jJPDs09IpUCVbafaPff2ut2rMRpaLIpX/0","content":"地位，声望，资质认证，经验，学术支持，法定，调研论证，这些具有使人信从的影响力和威望的属性都是权威度的衡量标准。<div><div>可信权威和可疑权威只是权威度的程度差别。</div><div><br></div><div>平台或环境根据权威度的衡量标准从可信到可疑的排序是：具有专业资质的和专业内认可度高的机构调研内容，论文，报纸，公众号，朋友圈。</div><div>每个平台和环境各自仍具有不同的权威度：专业资质认证（机构）＞野鸡（机构），行业认可＞一家之言，……</div><div><br></div><div>所以，权威的可信程度，可以用一些专业向、理性向、法定向的属性来加分判断。属性清晰的自然比刻意模糊的更具权威性。</div><div>另外，没有绝对的权威，对任何事情，我们都可以保持怀疑。</div><div><br></div></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8887,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492752632000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"肖妮","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEr7NCrg3Xcvj9ibStLd2Il6cXKwop7ll3fRfrLXQSK8CN9x1WMNHGziaH5P7sGUwUWUia8Dab9c6QP2/0","content":"可靠权威：专业第三方机构，权威机构的数据调查分析，权威专家/机构<div>理由：真实、客观、专业</div><div><br></div><div>可疑的权威：未经认证的公众号/大师/XXX专家/某些团体得出的结论</div><div>理由：一家之言，无从考证，未经查验证实</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8821,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492738015000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"清凉","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Aywp6DnlibkTWhYxTTUddSuWN1D2JZ3Ruokp8RpQ7HDtQ2dgJmmogtiask40PKkb2yVt5oBCxIzZG6Z/0","content":"可信权威: 在某一领域公认的，有影响力的具体一位专家或团队。例如 调理脾胃: 西苑医院肠胃科某位大夫是可信权威。<div>可疑权威:笼统性的泛称，或者在跨行的权威，公众人物等。例如 调理脾胃:某中医说某运动医学专家；于丹。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8815,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492737292000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"罗磊","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoCv1vtHZcnrZ8l6iaZ4oRlSs5kqGtyCASniaAibfjEoViaYNyXiaLDhzTeBbYQaOicj2oK3rW78yXrNtHr/0","content":"如何区分可信和可疑权威？这也是我的问题，凭自己的经验和知识来辨别吗？有些问题拿到度娘那里，也会翻到相悖的观点。<div><br></div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8772,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492728497000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jojo","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLDEdHiaL8iahBI6p5R3BoCzw3MmCgRVZvE5faOkojIVoAH1YK3XlRibCjb11yBLN3RLIcLIpVLOkNMLQ/0","content":"？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8739,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492707612000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"一六八","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98Wj5962gAwV3yia9fHQQe9zx3iaibxmrt3HcBF7V8tibic9BuL8bjibqOOGyicRBo9icOaFmXf7Q7c5VxPWuQic6QK1nVqJR/0","content":"（1）可信权威<div>一位中医医师指出要早睡早起，这样才有益健康。</div><div>（2）可疑权威</div><div>一位专家指出，人体睡眠质量不足可以通过午觉补回来。</div><div><br></div><div>以上可信权威是有科学依据的。</div><div>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 可疑权威是没有任何科学依据的，人体只有在晚上脏腑才会进行休息，拥有足够的睡眠配合脏腑的休息。这时候淋巴等其他代谢功能进行代谢。而午觉虽说可以补充精神，但是身体的脏腑已经因为睡眠不足而过度运转了。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8737,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492707219000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"青青枣实～","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/UPj0egwhddG46evSjhoopsDOglJ7YDNJTysd8ZXpLppVibia3UjtV3rAsibHvE3RxfbTrxP1BIFxdRpR6LrLPUahp0GibZUNPGy6/0","content":"<div>1、可信权威：</div><div>爱因斯坦相对论</div><div>可靠原因：得到科学的论证和时间的检验</div><div><br></div><div>2、可疑权威：</div><div>大V 的产品推荐</div><div>可疑原因：</div><div>(1)利益冲突：大V 也营销企业可能有利益关系，可获得推广费用;</div><div>(2)知识盲点：大V 不见得对产品有深入了解和体验，可能未涉及过该行业，不懂该产品行业产品全方位的评判标准。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8680,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492700115000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小思\uD83D\uDE0A","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6Yvr7MV0HZuArNEDF5MvP23BzKicTxtEBsFn9XbZgvJibW4hctx2MqFpI1fnice3iayTZDiclDtOqbnkV3xGsu49asKT/0","content":"现在大家用的微信公众号都多，这个“公众”就让人觉得有权威的感觉。从我过去带娃学习经验来看，可信的育儿公众号对每个主题时，会引经据典，逻辑清楚，有时还会辟谣，如“一小时爸爸”；可疑的育儿公众号呈文多是标题党，内容泛泛，东摘西抄还总在卖各种团购的，如曾以崔医生冠名的某号。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8665,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492698003000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"海岸线一圈","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjGXG4LIAqypP7xjnAekdibrbpsgkrS2KZS0uUopdqPt692QRhiaianNYI0jtElT3fbjEZwvxWtFBoiaF/0","content":"<p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nfont-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">可信的权威：</span></p><ol><li style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\n     text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\n     mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">经过反复论证实践的经典著作</span></li><li style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\n     text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\n     mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">行业内有一定声誉和成功经验的权威人士</span></li><li style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\n     text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\n     mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">有大量证据支持、论证严密、逻辑清晰的报告</span></li><li style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\n     text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\n     tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\n     mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">公认的秉持公正严肃报道风格的媒体</span></li></ol><p style=\"text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;text-ali